PN,37801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774465894
OL,3,CDrug dealer who stamped mother-of-two
OL,4,Cto death jailed for murder
OL,6,FChukwuemeka Ahanonu, 23, drove the
OL,7,Fwrong way on a busy Leicester road
OL,8,Fbefore crashing and overturning his
OL,9,Fcar. Minutes later, he murdered Nila
OL,10,FPatel, 56, after she got off the bus
OL,11,Fand was chatting on the phone to her
OL,12,Ffriend as she walked along the road.
OL,14,FA drug dealer who stamped on a 56-year-
OL,15,Fold woman in a random attack has been
OL,16,Fjailed for her murder.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774465894
OL,3,CDrug dealer who stamped mother-of-two
OL,4,Cto death jailed for murder
OL,6,FChukwuemeka Ahanonu, 23, was a
OL,7,Fstranger to mother Nila Patel, who
OL,8,Fdied in hospital two days after he
OL,9,Fattacked her in Leicester, leaving her
OL,10,Fwith brain damage.
OL,12,FThe fatal attack happened after
OL,13,FAhanonu crashed and overturned the BMW
OL,14,Fhe was driving, near to the Leicester
OL,15,FRoyal Infirmary on 24 June 2025.
OL,17,FMs Patel had just got off a bus and
OL,18,Fwas talking on her phone to a friend
OL,19,Fas she walked along the road.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774465894
OL,3,CDrug dealer who stamped mother-of-two
OL,4,Cto death jailed for murder
OL,6,FThe trial at Leicester Crown Court,
OL,7,Fheard that Ahanonu, of Dover Street,
OL,8,FLeicester, punched Ms Patel in the
OL,9,Fface with such severity that she fell
OL,10,Fonto the pavement. She was then kicked
OL,11,Fand stamped on as she lay on the floor.
OL,13,FAhanonu has been jailed for 21 years
OL,14,Fand six months at Leicester Crown
OL,15,FCourt for the murder Ms Patel in the
OL,16,Fcity last year.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774465894
OL,3,CDrug dealer who stamped mother-of-two
OL,4,Cto death jailed for murder
OL,6,FEarlier in the trial, the jury was
OL,7,Ftold former university student Ahanonu
OL,8,Fwas freed from a two-year sentence in
OL,9,FJuly 2024, having been found with more
OL,10,Fthan #1,000 in cash and a machete
OL,11,Fafter going through a red light in
OL,12,FSeptember 2023.
OL,14,FProsecutors said that on the day of
OL,15,Fthe 'vicious attack', a blood test for
OL,16,Fcannabis showed Ahanonu was almost
OL,17,Ffour times the legal limit for driving.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774465894
OL,3,CDrug dealer who stamped mother-of-two
OL,4,Cto death jailed for murder
OL,6,FNo alcohol was found in a blood sample
OL,7,Ftaken around three hours after the
OL,8,Fmurder, but a test for THC, which is
OL,9,Fproduced by cannabis use, found a
OL,10,Flevel of 7.6mcg, above the limit of
OL,11,F2mcg.
OL,13,FProsecutor Mary Prior KC had told
OL,14,Fjurors that Ms Patel, who was 5ft 4in
OL,15,Ftall, was "viciously attacked" by
OL,16,FAhanonu, who was claiming universal
OL,17,Fcredit despite running a "significant"
OL,18,Fdrugs business.
OL,26,@wD@KOUwD@^O]yD@ZOUyD@fO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774465894
OL,3,CDrug dealer who stamped mother-of-two
OL,4,Cto death jailed for murder
OL,6,FAlleging that the defendant had acted
OL,7,Fas he did because he had taken a lot
OL,8,Fof cannabis, Ms Prior told the jury:
OL,9,F"The voluntary consumption of a
OL,10,Fsubstance which causes you to act in a
OL,11,Fway that you would not act when sober
OL,12,Fis not a defence to murder because an
OL,13,Fintoxicated intent is still an intent."
OL,15,FMs Prior had told the trial: "She (Ms
OL,16,FPatel) had just got off the bus on her
OL,17,Fway home and was walking along the
OL,18,Froad, talking on the telephone to her
OL,19,Fdear friend.
OL,26,@qD@AOUuD@gO]wD@^OU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774465894
OL,3,CDrug dealer who stamped mother-of-two
OL,4,Cto death jailed for murder
OL,6,F"She was pulled from behind by the
OL,7,Fdefendant, punched in the face with
OL,8,Fsuch severity that she fell onto the
OL,9,Fpavement. She was then kicked and
OL,10,Fstamped on as she lay on the floor...
OL,11,Fstamped on her face."
OL,13,FDetective Inspector Emma Matts, of
OL,14,FLeicestershire Police, said: "Ahanonu
OL,15,Fwas unknown to Ms Patel. After
OL,16,Fcrashing his vehicle, he ran from the
OL,17,Fscene violently attacking Ms Patel.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@UO]vD@^OU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774465894
OL,3,CDrug dealer who stamped mother-of-two
OL,4,Cto death jailed for murder
OL,6,F"This was the most horrific, violent
OL,7,Fand random attack by a stranger on a
OL,8,Fkind, gentle and loving woman who was
OL,9,Fsimply making her way home.
OL,11,F"It is hard to imagine what Ms Patel
OL,12,Fwent through in those moments. My
OL,13,Fthoughts continue to remain with her
OL,14,Fand with her family and friends who
OL,15,Fhave suffered and continue to suffer
OL,16,Fthe most horrendous distress and pain."
OL,18,FMs Patel's son and daughter ` Jaidan
OL,19,Fand Danika Patel - described their mum
OL,20,Fas their "best friend and biggest
OL,21,Fsupporter".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@gO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774465894
OL,3,CDrug dealer who stamped mother-of-two
OL,4,Cto death jailed for murder
OL,6,FIn a statement, they said: "Our mum
OL,7,Fwas not just a name in this case. She
OL,8,Fwas a loving mother, a daughter, a
OL,9,Fsister, a friend, and the heart of our
OL,10,Ffamily. She was our best friend and
OL,11,Four biggest supporter. Since the day
OL,12,Fshe was taken from us, our lives have
OL,13,Fbeen changed forever. We are still
OL,14,Ftrying to process the shock and trauma
OL,15,Fof losing mum in such a sudden and
OL,16,Fviolent way.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774465894
OL,3,CDrug dealer who stamped mother-of-two
OL,4,Cto death jailed for murder
OL,6,F"Mum was a single mother who faced
OL,7,Fmany obstacles and hardships
OL,8,Fthroughout her life ` challenges that
OL,9,Fwould have broken most people. Yet no
OL,10,Fmatter what she went through, she
OL,11,Fwould still end each day with a smile
OL,12,Fbright enough to lift the mood of
OL,13,Feveryone around her.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774465894
OL,3,CDrug dealer who stamped mother-of-two
OL,4,Cto death jailed for murder
OL,6,F"She was quiet, gentle, funny, kind,
OL,7,Floving and deeply caring. She always
OL,8,Fput others before herself and she
OL,9,Fnever expected anything in return.
OL,10,FWhat truly made her happy was making
OL,11,Fthe people around her feel loved `
OL,12,Fwhether that was through a thoughtful
OL,13,Fgift, a warm meal she had cooked, or
OL,14,Fone of the sweet desserts she loved to
OL,15,Fmake for us.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774465894
OL,3,CDrug dealer who stamped mother-of-two
OL,4,Cto death jailed for murder
OL,6,F"Mum still had so much life ahead of
OL,7,Fher. She should have had the chance to
OL,8,Fgrow old, to enjoy retirement, to
OL,9,Fbecome a grandmother and to celebrate
OL,10,Fmany more milestones with her family.
OL,11,FAll of those moments have now been
OL,12,Ftaken away from her ` and from us.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774465894
OL,3,CDrug dealer who stamped mother-of-two
OL,4,Cto death jailed for murder
OL,6,F"The cruelty and senselessness of what
OL,7,Fhappened on that day in June last year
OL,8,Fis something we will forever struggle
OL,9,Fto come to terms. The fact that mum
OL,10,Fwas concerned about the defendant
OL,11,Fafter his crash shows exactly the type
OL,12,Fof person she was. Even in that
OL,13,Fmoment, her instinct was to care about
OL,14,Fsomeone else. There isn't a day goes
OL,15,Fby where we don't think about her,
OL,16,Fmiss her or wish we could speak to her
OL,17,Fjust one more time. Nothing prepares
OL,18,Fyou for the moment you realise that
OL,19,Fsomeone you love so deeply has been
OL,20,Ftaken from you.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774465894
OL,3,CDrug dealer who stamped mother-of-two
OL,4,Cto death jailed for murder
OL,6,F"We will carry mum's love, her
OL,7,Fguidance, her kindness and the memory
OL,8,Fof who she was with us every day for
OL,9,Fthe rest of our lives and we will
OL,10,Fnever stop wishing the world could
OL,11,Fhave had more of her in it.
OL,13,F"Mum's life mattered."
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/14
